{"comments":"Buffer Pool — GPU Buffer Pooling with Size Buckets\n\n## Purpose\n\nGPU buffer allocation is expensive. This module provides:\n\n- **Size-bucketed pooling**: Reuse buffers by size class\n- **Free list management**: O(1) acquire/release\n- **Memory statistics**: Track allocation patterns\n\n## Bucket Strategy\n\nBuffers are allocated in power-of-4 sizes (1KB, 4KB, 16KB, ...):\n- Reduces fragmentation\n- Enables fast bucket lookup\n- Supports custom sizes for large allocations\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nBuffer pools reduce per-frame allocation to near-zero:\n- Agents share buffer pools within render contexts\n- Reuse rate approaches 100% for steady-state workloads\n- Custom buckets handle outlier sizes without fragmentation\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[132,3]},"title":"Bucket1KB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[133,3]},"title":"Bucket4KB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[134,3]},"title":"Bucket16KB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"Bucket64KB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"Bucket256KB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Resource/Buffer.purs","start":[137,3]},"title":"Bucket1MB"},{"comments":null,"in